# UI & UX (Compose Multiplatform)

Product focus: **household nutrition logistics** (grocery + meal plan + local AI assistant). Home shows nutrition hub; Adventures/Budget are coming-soon only.

## Layout & scrolling

- Tokens: `ScreenLayout` (`horizontalPadding` 24dp, `sectionSpacing` 16dp, `expandedMinWidth` 600dp, `expandedSidePanelWidth` 340dp).
- Screen body: `Modifier.screenContentArea(padding)` + `screenListPadding()`.
- Lists with sticky input: `NutritionScaffold` `bottomBar` on phone; side panel when `maxWidth >= expandedMinWidth` (grocery).
- `imePadding()` on scrollable content and input bars; `JourneySnackbarHost(aboveBottomBar = …)` when bottom bar visible.
- Wide layouts: `BoxWithConstraints`; test grocery + meal plan at ≥600dp and phone fallback.

## Design system — use these (shipped)

### Journey primitives (required for new UI)

| Component | Use |
|-----------|-----|
| `JourneyPrimaryButton` / `Secondary` / `Tertiary` | Action hierarchy |
| `JourneyDestructiveOutlinedButton` / `DestructiveTextButton` | Sign out, delete, clear irreversible |
| `JourneyTextField` | All user-facing forms (56dp min, `isError`, `supportingText`) |
| `JourneyIconButton` | 48×48dp icon actions |
| `JourneyLoadingContent` / `JourneyErrorContent` / `JourneyEmptyState` | Async and empty UX |
| `JourneySnackbarHost` | Snackbars above grocery bottom bar |
| `JourneyBanner` | Inline notices |

### Family logistics & chrome

- Surfaces: `FamilyLogisticsCardSurface`, `FamilyLogisticCard`, `FamilyLogisticsSectionHeader`, `NutritionFeatureHeader`
- Nutrition: `NutritionScaffold`, `GroceryInputBar`, `GroceryItemRow`, `MealPlanDayCard`, `MealPlanEmptyState`
- AI read-only: `AiReadOnlyGroceryList`, `AiGrocerySuggestionsSection` — terracotta accent (`AiReadOnlyAccent`), never mixed with editable rows
- **Tab & hero icons:** `MainTabIconArt` — transparent WebP glyphs shared by bottom nav (`MainTabIconDefaults.tabIconSize` 32dp) and Today hero circles (`heroIconSize` 48dp). Map nutrition features via `NutritionFeatureKind.toMainTabIconKind()`.
- **Member avatars:** `MemberAvatar` — circular photo or initials on Family members rows; tap-to-upload when permitted (48dp default).
- Background: `NapolitanBackground` inside `AppTheme`
- Viewer: `HouseholdViewerReadOnlyNotice` when `canWriteHouseholdData` is false

### Colors & theme

- Palettes: `SharedJourneyColors` + `sharedJourneyLightScheme()` / `sharedJourneyDarkScheme()`
- **Semantic (theme-aware):** `JourneySemanticColors.inkDeep()`, `inkMuted()`, `cardSurface()`, `elevatedSurface()` — use on glass/surfaces in dark mode
- Static brand: `TerracottaOrange`, `MediterraneanTeal`, `InkSecondary` for subtitles (not `InkDeep.copy(alpha=…)`)
- Icons: `AppIcons` only — no `Icons.Default` in presentation

### Typography (`AppTheme.kt`)

Roles defined: `displaySmall`, `headlineMedium`, `titleLarge/Medium/Small`, `bodyLarge/Medium/Small`, `labelLarge/Medium/Small`. Body line height ~1.5×.

### Touch targets

- Minimum **48×48dp** — `JourneyIconButton`, `FamilyLogisticsDesign.minTouchTarget`, `FeatureAccentIconButton`
- Grocery rows: `heightIn(min = 56.dp)`

## Button hierarchy

| Variant | When |
|---------|------|
| Primary (teal) | One main forward action per section |
| Secondary (outlined) | Alternate path |
| Tertiary (`TextButton`) | Cancel, dismiss |
| Destructive (terracotta) | Irreversible — confirm in dialog |

Loading: disable control + small `CircularProgressIndicator` in button; no duplicate full-screen spinner for same action.

## UX state patterns

| State | Pattern |
|-------|---------|
| Loading | `JourneyLoadingContent` or button spinner; spinner color `MediterraneanTeal` |
| Error | `JourneyErrorContent` + retry, or snackbar for async |
| Empty | `JourneyEmptyState` with icon + optional CTA + `testTag` |
| Success | Snackbar (undo where applicable) |

- **AI data:** read-only sections with subtitle; editable list separate; adopt flows explicit.
- **Pull-to-refresh:** grocery + meal plan via `NutritionScreenModel.refresh()`.
- **Haptics:** `rememberJourneyHapticFeedback()` — light click on grocery toggle (Android; iOS no-op until wired).
- **Route transitions:** `AnimatedContent` in `App.kt` (subtle horizontal slide).

## Strings & accessibility

- `i18n-multilingual.mdc`: 8 locales, `stringResource` in composables only.
- `contentDescription` on meaningful icons; `null` only when decorative duplicate.
- Icon semantics: `Sparkles` = AI only; `CheckCircle`/`RadioButtonUnchecked` = grocery check state; chevrons = expand/nav.

## Testability

- `*TestTags` objects per feature (`MealPlanTestTags`, `GroceryInputBarTestTags`, `GroceryListTestTags`, etc.).
- Empty/loading/error: stable `testTag` when user-visible.
- Instrumented tests use tags, not display text.

## Anti-patterns

- Hardcoded English; `stringResource` in `LaunchedEffect`/callbacks.
- Raw `OutlinedTextField`, raw `IconButton` without 48dp, one-off hex colors.
- Business logic in `@Composable`; duplicate gate loading/error columns.
- Phone-only grocery bottom bar on wide screens (use side panel + hide bottom bar).
- Teal accent on AI read-only cards (use terracotta).

## Do not regress (Waves A–C complete)

Journey form controls on all screens; home/nutrition gates use Journey loading/error; inline validation on login/join; snackbars above grocery input; pull-to-refresh; dark theme follow system; wide grocery/meal plan layouts; locale parity tests green.
